<title>UK: UBS sets call warrants on Novartis.</title>
<headline>UBS sets call warrants on Novartis.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-02-13</dateline>
<text>
<p>Union Bank of Switzerland said it has issued 20 million American-style call warrants on registered shares of Novartis AG.</p>
<p>One share is controlled by 50 warrants.</p>
<p> STRIKE PRICE    1,850 CHF		 PREMIUM	13.3 PCT</p>
<p> ISSUE PRICE     2.60 CHF		  GEARING	13.4 TIMES</p>
<p> EXERCISE PERIOD 21.FEB.97-18.WEP.98   PAYDATE	21.FEB.97</p>
<p> LISTING	   SWISS		     MIN EXER LOT 100</p>
<p> SPOT REFERENCE  1,746 CHF</p>
<p>--Reuter London Newsroom +44 171 542 7658</p>
</text>
